/artists/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a> 。您可以在下面看到完整的曲目列表，并在上面观看<em>《克拉伦斯之书》</em>的官方预告片。</p><p> <strong>01 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;All About You&#39; (ft. Jorge Ben Jor)</strong><br /> <strong>02 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;Hallelujah Heaven&#39;（ft. Lil Wayne、Buju Banton 和 Shabba Ranks）</strong><br /> <strong>03 Jeymes Samuel / Doja Cat / Kodak Black – &#39;Jeezu&#39; (ft. Adekunle Gold)</strong><br /> <strong>04 Jeymes Samuel – “香槟”（ft. Jorja Smith）</strong><br /> <strong>05 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;Sacred Love&#39; (ft. Yemi Alade)</strong><br /> <strong>06 Jeymes Samuel / D&#39;Angelo / Jay-Z –“我想要你永远”</strong><br /> <strong>07 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;Godqueen&#39; (ft. Kid Cudi)</strong><br /> <strong>08 杰梅斯·塞缪尔 – 《亲爱的天堂》</strong><br /> <strong>09 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;Magdalene&#39; (ft. Alice Smith)</strong><br /> <strong>10 Jeymes Samuel – &#39;Varinia&#39; (ft. Terry Callier)</strong><br /> <strong>11 杰梅斯·塞缪尔 – 《拿撒勒》</strong></p><p>早在 10 月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-z-opens-up-about-the-battle-to-get-his-masters-it-was-the-fight-of-my-life-3524208">Jay-Z 就公开了争取主人的战斗，称“这是他一生中的战斗”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-z-and-dangelo-to-release-collaborative-new-song-this-week-3568250">Jay-Z 和 D&#39;Angelo 将于本周发布合作新歌的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
