e.com/artists/phish">Phish</a>乐队）和 Classic TAB、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a>和 The Sleeping Souls、Jessie Murph、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d4vd">d4vd</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bad-rabbits-share-powerful-new-video-for-previously-released-wwyd-2691132">Bad Rabbits</a>等。</p><p>最后一天，杀手乐队 (The Killers) 将成为音乐节的主角。他们将与 Hozier、Megan Thee Stallion、The Revivalists、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lovejoy">Lovejoy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royel-otis">Royel Otis</a>等一起演奏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3450005" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3450005" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3450005" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2023 年波士顿召唤音乐节期间的石器时代女王" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Queens-Of-The-Stone-Age@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3450005" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年波士顿召唤音乐节期间石器时代的女王们。图片来源：Astrida Valigorsky/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>去年的版本中出现了许多头条新闻，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens of the Stone Age</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lumineers">The Lumineers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">Alanis Morissette</a> 。</p><p>我们在音乐节上尝试了 Foo Fighters 的演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/foo-fighters-live-at-boston-calling-an-emotional-return-3448804">我们给了四颗星</a>：“如果说 Foo Fighters 重新焕发了活力，那就意味着他们之前在某种程度上已经开始衰落，但 Freese 为他们的声音增添了新的维度和动力，让他们的声音更加出色。”他们的光滑和重量肯定会让他们成为摇滚乐的中流砥柱。”</p><p>更多行动即将公布。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boston-calling-2024-ed-sheeran-the-killers-hozier-megan-thee-stallion-and-more-for-stacked-line-up-3567934">波士顿的邮政致电2024：埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran），杀手，霍齐尔（Hozier），梅根·泰恩（Megan Thee）种马和更多宣布的堆积阵容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
